        <abstract> 
<p>Acknowledges StGJM’s kind letter. [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">7451</hi>.]</p>  
<p>Offers to alter the "dogmatic assertion" referred to on page 102 [of StGJM’s <hi rend="italic">On the genesis of species</hi>] but in 5th ed. of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> and in <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> CD finds only qualified expressions.</p> 
        </abstract>
